@startuml hand-off-session-state-machine

title hand_off_session — 6 entity 并行 state 联动 (双模式 / adopt / task 三态 / cleanup)

' ─── entity 1: caller session (DB) ───
state "Caller session\n(callerSid in sessions table)" as CallerState {
  state "active (lifecycle)" as CallerActive
  state "archived\n(archived_at = ISO ts)" as CallerArchived

  [*] --> CallerActive
  CallerActive --> CallerArchived : phase 2 archiveSourceSessionWithEmit\n(default archive_caller=true)
  CallerActive --> CallerActive : archive_caller=false (skip)\nphase 2.archived='skipped'
  CallerArchived --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 2: new session (DB + in-memory SDK) ───
state "New session (newSid)" as NewState {
  state "spawned\n(spawnSessionHandler 起 SDK subprocess)" as NewSpawned
  state "active + own caller tasks\n(post task reassign 三态)" as NewActive

  [*] --> NewSpawned : spawn (handOffMode=true)\n跳过 spawn-guards / 不写 spawn-link
  NewSpawned --> NewActive : phase 1.6 task reassign\n(clear-team / preserve-team / skip)
  NewActive --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 3: teammate sessions (DB + in-memory SDK) ───
state "Teammate sessions\n(caller 同 team 内 active+dormant)" as TeammateState {
  state "active / dormant" as TeammateAlive
  state "swapped (adopt path)\n与 newSid 共享 active team" as TeammateAdopted
  state "closed\n(baton cleanup phase 1)" as TeammateClosed

  [*] --> TeammateAlive
  TeammateAlive --> TeammateAdopted : adopt_teammates=true\nphase 1.5 swapLead 完成
  note left of TeammateAdopted
    与 newSid 共享 active team
    可继续 send_message 沟通
    phase 1 skip (skipped='adopt-keep-implicit')
  end note
  TeammateAlive --> TeammateClosed : adopt_teammates=false (default)\nphase 1 shutdownTeammatesOnBaton
  note right of TeammateClosed
    REVIEW_36 R2 HIGH-A:
    excludeSessionIds 显式排除 newSid
    防 team_name=x baton 路径下新 session
    被 spawn 加为 teammate 然后一并 close
  end note
  TeammateAdopted --> [*]
  TeammateClosed --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 4: team_members.role (DB) ───
state "team_members.role\n(per team)" as RoleState {
  state "caller: lead\n+ teammate: teammate" as RoleOrig
  state "newSid: lead\n+ teammate: teammate\n(caller role 移除)" as RoleSwapped
  state "team archived\n(无 lead role)" as RoleArchived

  [*] --> RoleOrig
  RoleOrig --> RoleSwapped : adopt_teammates=true\nphase 1.5 swapLead per team
  RoleOrig --> RoleArchived : adopt_teammates=false\n(default 纯 baton: caller archive 后\nteam 无 lead → 走 TeamLifecycleScheduler\n30min grace 自动 archive)
  RoleSwapped --> [*]
  RoleArchived --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 5: task ownership (DB tasks.owner_session_id + tasks.team_id) ───
state "Task ownership\n(per caller-owned task)" as TaskState {
  state "owner=caller\n+ team_id=<original> | NULL" as TaskOrig
  state "owner=newSid\n+ team_id=NULL\n(clear-team default)" as TaskClearedTeam
  state "owner=newSid\n+ team_id 不动\n(preserve-team)" as TaskPreservedTeam
  state "deleted (team task)\n+ owner=newSid (personal task)\n(skip policy)" as TaskSkip

  [*] --> TaskOrig
  TaskOrig --> TaskClearedTeam : team_task_policy='clear-team' (default)\nUPDATE owner + team_id=NULL
  TaskOrig --> TaskPreservedTeam : team_task_policy='preserve-team'\nUPDATE owner 不动 team_id
  note right of TaskPreservedTeam
    caller 自负责任:
    如 newSid 没成为对应 team active member
    → newSid 撞写权限 reject
    handler ok return.taskReassignment.policyWarning
    = 'preserve-team-unadopted-teams' + unadoptedTeamIds
  end note
  TaskOrig --> TaskSkip : team_task_policy='skip'\n单 transaction 4 步原子\n(SELECT → DELETE team task → cleanup blocks → reassign personal)
  TaskOrig --> TaskOrig : archive_caller=false\n(task 仍 owner=caller,后续 CASCADE GC 删)

  TaskClearedTeam --> [*]
  TaskPreservedTeam --> [*]
  TaskSkip --> [*]
}

' ─── entity 6: spawn-link (DB sessions.spawned_by / spawn_depth) ───
state "spawn-link 关系\n(caller → newSid)" as SpawnLinkState {
  state "未记录\n(newSid.spawned_by = null)" as NoLink
  note right of NoLink
    hand_off 是平级接力非派遣关系
    handOffMode=true → spawn handler 永不写 spawn-link
    SessionList Phase C 树形分组不挂 teammate badge
    与普通 spawn_session 行为不同(后者写 spawn-link)
  end note

  [*] --> NoLink
  NoLink --> [*]
}

' ─── 跨 entity 时序串联 (CHANGELOG_99 双模式 + Phase 6 adopt 路径) ───

note as N1
  hand_off_session tool **6 entity 联动**:

  ① Caller: CallerActive → (archive_caller=true) → CallerArchived
  ② New session: [*] → NewSpawned → NewActive (post task reassign)
  ③ Teammate: TeammateAlive → (adopt=true) → TeammateAdopted | (default) → TeammateClosed
  ④ team_members.role: RoleOrig → (adopt=true) → RoleSwapped | (default) → RoleArchived (scheduler 30min grace)
  ⑤ Task: TaskOrig → (policy 三态) → TaskClearedTeam | TaskPreservedTeam | TaskSkip
  ⑥ spawn-link: 永不写 (handOffMode=true 与 spawn_session 普通路径区别)

  **双模式差异** (CHANGELOG_99):
  - plan-driven: 5 entity 全联动 + cwd resilience (默认 mainRepo)
  - generic: 同 5 entity 联动 + cwd 默认 caller cwd + phaseLabel/plan_file_path silently ignored

  **失败兜底**:
  - spawn 失败 → 6 entity 全停在 [*] / TaskOrig / TeammateAlive (无变更)
  - phase 1.5 firstTeam swap 失败 → closeSession(newSid) 回滚 + REJECT (新 session 也撤回)
  - phase 1.5 非 firstTeam swap 失败 → adopted.failed 软失败 + 其他 team 继续
  - phase 1.6 task reassign throw → warn 不阻塞 + taskReassignment.status='failed'
  - phase 2 archive caller throw → archived='failed' warn-only,5 entity 中 caller 仍 active

  **与 archive_plan baton 时序对比**:
  - hand_off: spawn newSid → reassignTaskOwner → phase 1 (teammate close) → phase 2 (archive caller)
  - archive_plan: Step 1-7 (plan/worktree/branch 收口) → phase 1 (teammate close) → phase 2 (archive caller)
  - 共享 runBatonCleanup helper (phase 1+2),核心差异: hand_off 有 spawn + task reassign,archive_plan 无
end note

@enduml
